data.description: This Wilderness Hills 2-story home is in tip-top shape and ready for its new owners. A home office with French doors is located right off the stunning entrance. The entry flows into an open living room, dining, and kitchen space. Granite countertops, an under-mounted sink, and a huge walk-in pantry are just a few of the impressive details in the kitchen. The main level has been updated with porcelain wood tile for added durability and style. The open feel of this home continues on the 2nd Level with a large loft space overlooking the foyer. In addition to 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, you will find a laundry room, a tile walk-in Shower, jetted tub, and flex room off the master suite. A 4th bedroom and bathroom are located in the basement along with a wet bar and ample storage space. A fully fenced yard and covered deck round out the outdoor living space. The final perk not to be missed on this home is the 4 stall garage!  Schedule your showing today!
